  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I think I took it out from his pocket, and I kept it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he looked normal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was tanned and all that, so I put it in front of his face.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know who the man was that was separating left to right, but I understood that he's looking for people to go to work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I kept this picture in front of my father's face.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, Schneider Meister, Schneider Meister, and he took him with the living.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I wore a navy blouse with a zipper that my father made-- he dyed linen, white linen to cover-- I think I mentioned it before.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't know where I got the idea.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I took a needle with white thread and on the pocket, I wound it around like that and telling him, also Schneider.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At that time it was '42.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was a Schneider like I'm a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But anyway, I knew a little bit, of course, I grew up around it and I worked already in the Lask ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we were taken with, I think about 300 people-- I  don't remember exactly how many-- we were taken out of town, which was really maybe a kilometer away, and put in a big ditch.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And around that ditch, there were these guards standing with guns, but it was already dark, so it really-- and we cuddled together and this is how we stay there overnight, in that ditch.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the morning-- I don't remember if it was one night or two nights.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "God, memory lapses.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we're taken out in groups of 20. 20, 30, it was  very small groups.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
